title: High concentrations reported at 8:00, 05/19/2016
body: __Update for May 19, 2016 at 10:01 CST.__ There is 1 monitoring site reporting a 1-hr AQI above 85. The maximum 1-hr AQI of 93 (PM2.5) was reported at Davenport, Hayes Sch [AQS ID: 191630020] by the **Iowa DNR**. Learn more at AQI Watch.
